OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAberpergwm: Coal mine      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexpansion facing legal     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fchallenge                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A legal challenge will go ahead into   
OL,6, mine expansion plans after opponents   
OL,7, were granted a judicial review.        
OL,9,FIn January approval was given for      
OL,10,Fanother 40 million tonnes of coal to be
OL,11,Fdug at Aberpergwm, Neath Port Talbot.  
OL,13,FCampaigners said at the time they were 
OL,14,Fconsidering legal action.              
OL,16,FThe Welsh government, which declined to
OL,17,Fcomment citing the legal proceedings,  
OL,18,Fhas previously called for an overhaul  
OL,19,Fof the Coal Authority following the    
OL,20,Fdispute over the plans.                
